---
id: my_agent_21
name: Basic Agent
description: A basic prompt that uses the gpt-4o chat API to answer questions
metadata:
  authors:
    - sethjuarez
    - mwhalin
  tags:
    - basic
    - gpt-4o

model:
  id: 2024-05-01-preview

inputs:
  name:
    type: string
    sample: User
    description: The name of the customer
  question:
    type: string
    sample: What is (1+3)/2?
    required: true
    description: The question to answer

tools:
  - name: coder
    runtime: server
    type: code_interpreter
    configuration:
      file_ids:
        - code.py
        - params.json

template:
  format: mustache
  parser: prompty
---
system:
You are an AI assistant that can write code to help answer math questions.

user[name="{{name}}"]:
{{question}}

![thread]